k#\">Telepass</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.as24.com/nl\">Total</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.as24.com/nl\">Toll4Europe</a></li></ul>","en":"<p>All vehicles subject to the kilometre charge must be equipped with a switched-on OBU (On Board Unit) on all Belgian roads. You also must mention the right Euro emission norm in your OBU.</p><p>You can obtain an OBU from the following serviceproviders: </p><ul><li><a href=\"https://rup.satellic.be\">Satellic</a></li><li><a href=\"https://axxes.fr/fr\">Axxès</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.eurotoll.eu/fr\">Eurotoll</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.telepass.com/en/truck#\">Telepass</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.as24.com/nl\">Total</a></li><li><a href=\"https://toll4europe.eu/de\">Toll4Europe</a></li></ul>"},"@type":"Procedure","order":0}],"websites":[{"naam":{"nl-BE-x-formal":"Satellic","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Satellic","nl":"Satellic"},"url":"https://www.satellic.be/nl","@type":"Website","order":0},{"naam":{"nl-BE-x-formal":"Eurotoll ","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Eurotoll ","nl":"Eurotoll "},"url":"https://www.eurotoll.eu/fr","@type":"Website","order":1},{"naam":{"nl":"Viapass","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Viapass","nl-BE-x-formal":"Viapass"},"url":"https://www.viapass.be","@type":"Website","order":2},{"naam":{"nl":"TOTAL","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"TOTAL","nl-BE-x-formal":"TOTAL"},"url":"https://www.as24.com/nl","@type":"Website","order":3},{"naam":{"nl-BE-x-formal":"Toll4Europe","nl":"Toll4Europe","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Toll4Europe"},"url":"https://toll4europe.eu/de","@type":"Website","order":4},{"naam":{"nl":"Telepass ","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Telepass ","nl-BE-x-formal":"Telepass "},"url":"https://www.telepass.com/en/truck#","@type":"Website","order":5},{"naam":{"nl":"Viapass - Deutsch","nl-BE-x-formal":"Viapass - Deutsch","de":"Viapass - Deutsch","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Viapass - Deutsch"},"url":"https://www.viapass.be/de","@type":"Website","order":6},{"naam":{"nl-BE-x-formal"